    },
    {
      "start": 749.9,
      "end": 750.52,
      "text": "비행기 탄다."
    },
    {
      "start": 750.78,
      "end": 751.52,
      "text": "그러게 되겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.06,
      "end": 752.48,
      "text": "Uh-oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.7,
      "end": 753.32,
      "text": "알겠지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 753.44,
      "end": 754.2,
      "text": "이걸로 바꿀게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.32,
      "end": 755.04,
      "text": "그러니까, all right."
    },
    {
      "start": 755.12,
      "end": 755.88,
      "text": "부드러운 말투인데."
    },
    {
      "start": 755.88,
      "end": 756.48,
      "text": "All right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.62,
      "end": 757.48,
      "text": "All right, honey?"
    },
    {
      "start": 757.98,
      "end": 758.66,
      "text": "알겠지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.66,
      "end": 762.5,
      "text": "That's why you let me win today."
    },
    {
      "start": 762.7,
      "end": 764.92,
      "text": "Ah, she did let him win."
    },
    {
      "start": 765.04,
      "end": 765.5,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 765.8,
      "end": 767.3,
      "text": "The pizza making competition."
    },
    {
      "start": 767.52,
      "end": 768.58,
      "text": "음, 맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 769.22,
      "end": 771.68,
      "text": "That's why you let me win today."
    },
    {
      "start": 772.14,
      "end": 775.74,
      "text": "그래서 오늘 네가 나를 이기게 한 거잖아."
    },
    {
      "start": 776.28,
      "end": 777.18,
      "text": "라는 말이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.18,
      "end": 781.68,
      "text": "사실 이 timing이라는 것이 is very important한데"
    },
    {
      "start": 781.68,
      "end": 785.68,
      "text": "지금 레오가 살짝 늦은 감이 없잖아, 있기는 해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 785.88,
      "end": 786.08,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 786.08,
      "end": 793.02,
      "text": "네, 그래도 지금이라도 반성하고 이런 이야기를 하는 것이 얼마나 다행인가 싶습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 793.32,
      "end": 794.88,
      "text": "네, 비행기 표정은 아깝지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 795.22,
      "end": 796.5,
      "text": "Pay her back for it."
    },
    {
      "start": 796.56,
      "end": 797.12,
      "text": "아, 그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 797.2,
      "end": 798.5,
      "text": "And love her forever and ever."
    },
    {
      "start": 798.68,
      "end": 798.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 799.52,
      "end": 801.14,
      "text": "자, 이 장면 다시 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 801.8,
      "end": 802.84,
      "text": "I've changed."
    },
    {
      "start": 804.26,
      "end": 807.9,
      "text": "And I'm not afraid to tell you that I'm in love with you."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.69,
      "end": 809.65,
      "text": "I always have been."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.81,
      "end": 811.95,
      "text": "I always will be."
    },
    {
      "start": 812.75,
      "end": 816.29,
      "text": "I'm not afraid to tell my father that I want to start my own shop."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.55,
      "end": 816.75,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 816.75,
      "end": 818.57,
      "text": "It's about time."
    },
    {
      "start": 818.99,
      "end": 821.77,
      "text": "All this time, you never said anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 821.93,
      "end": 826.21,
      "text": "And now that I'm about to get on a plane, you finally find the words."
    },
    {
      "start": 826.65,
      "end": 827.65,
      "text": "Love isn't words."
    },
    {
      "start": 828.73,
      "end": 829.39,
      "text": "It's actions."
    },
    {
      "start": 830.8,
      "end": 831.1,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.28,
      "end": 832.76,
      "text": "That's why you let me win today."
    },
    {
      "start": 833.94,
      "end": 837.08,
      "text": "네, 송혜리님께서 메시지 보내주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 837.08,
      "end": 839.94,
      "text": "Screen English 시간 너무 즐거워요."
    },
    {
      "start": 839.94,
      "end": 841.94,
      "text": "조크쌤, 오늘도 감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 843.14,
      "end": 844.28,
      "text": "Oh, I'm glad you like it."
    },
    {
      "start": 844.32,
      "end": 845.18,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "start": 845.38,
      "end": 848.72,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 보람차게 Screen English 오늘 마무리를 해볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 848.86,
      "end": 849.82,
      "text": "Have a beautiful Wednesday."
    },
    {
      "start": 850.16,
      "end": 850.64,
      "text": "You too."
    }
  ]
